ugh the various community channels ([Twitter](https://twitter.com/gro_dao), [Medium](https://medium.com/gro-protocol), Discord, [Notion](https://www.notion.so/grodao/Gro-DAO-3cbc2435221f4a70b65d27392a35da03) and [Forum](https://community.gro.xyz/)) and community calls.\n\n### Composition\nRaambo will continue as the People Pod’s full-time facilitator while Jaypow, Kndlexi and Beckley will continue as part-time contributors.\n\nThe DAO community will also be incentivised to support on ad-hoc tasks via bounties.\n\n## Budget\nSee the [Budget & Composition](https://community.gro.xyz/t/grfc-people-pod-2nd-term-proposal/555#budget-composition-6) section of the GRFC for full details.\n\nIt is estimated that the People Pod will require 145,300 $USDC and 213,200 GRO to continue operating for another term.\n\nHowever, because the People Pod has an excess budget of 145,373 $USDC and 118,681 GRO from its 1st term, (if Vote 30 is accepted) it would only **require an additional 95,000 GRO (~$3,400 worth of GRO)** for its 2nd term.\n\n## Next Steps & Timeline\nVote 30 will run for 5 days on a simple majority basis. \n\nIf Vote 30 is passed, the People Pod’s 2nd 6-month term will run from July 19, 2023 - January 19, 2024.\n\nIf Vote 30 isn't passed, the People Pod will carefully review the proposal and engage in a thorough dialogue with the DAO community to incorporate any further feedback received to ultimately identify the most suitable solution that aligns with the DAO’s interests and expectations.",
