 30,000 USDC for any additional need for contributions (expenditure of this additional budget will always be synchronised with People Pod prior to spending).\n\nBecause its current term has ended with budget surplus of ~33,000 USDC and ~32,000 $GRO, if the proposed extension for a 2nd term is approved by the DAO, a total of 27,000 USDC + 8,000 $GRO will be transferred from the Gro DAO Treasury to the FiSt Pod's operational wallet.\n\n#### Reporting\nFiSt Pod will update the DAO on its progress via monthly reports and quarterly OKR reviews; and regularly through the community channels such as Community Forum, Discord, and Telegram.\n\n## Next Steps\nThis vote will run for 5 days on a simple majority basis.\n\nIf Vote 28 is passed, the FiSt Pod's multi-sig will be topped up with the requested amount, and its 2nd 6-month term will run from: July 10, 2023 - January 10, 2024.\n\nIf Vote 28 isn't passed, FiSt Pod will carefully review the proposal and engage in a thorough dialogue with the community to incorporate any further feedback received to ultimately identify the most suitable solution that aligns with the community’s interests and expectations.",
