ing process\n\n**FOR**: Approve the strategy for whitelist on Gro protocol\n**AGAINST**: Do not approve the strategy for whitelist on Gro protocol\n**ABSTAIN**: No opinion on approving this strategy for whitelist on Gro protocol \n\n### Next steps\n\nThis vote will run for **3 days**.\n\nEach strategy that receives majority approval (ignoring abstain votes) will be added to the protocol whitelist, meaning there is DAO authority to allocate protocol funds (within the maximum Vault exposures).\n\nFuture strategies can be suggested and voted on by the DAO, and at any time community members can also propose a removal of a strategy from the current whitelist.\n",
